             was indicted for <rs id="t18120408-8-off39" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18120408-8-off39" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18120408-8-off39" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
